 <h3>Platform security layers</h3>
 <p>We at Robopragma Pro protect your account and funds through industry-standard encryption and verification. All data transmitted between your device and our servers uses SSL encryption — a technology that scrambles your information so it cannot be intercepted. During account creation, we collect your identity and address information through our KYC (Know Your Customer) verification process. This step typically takes subject to verification and confirms your eligibility to use the platform. We store all personal data in secure, encrypted databases. Two-factor authentication is available for added security — enable it in your account settings to require a second verification step during login. Your password should be unique and complex; never share it with anyone. If you suspect unauthorized access, reset your password immediately and contact our English support team. All transactions — deposits, withdrawals, and game activity — are logged and encrypted. You can review your complete transaction history anytime from your account dashboard.</p>

 <h3>Game fairness and RTP</h3>
 <p>We at Robopragma Pro operate two distinct game categories, each with different fairness mechanisms. Live-dealer tables are broadcast in real time from professional HD studios. Professional dealers conduct all games — Baccarat, Roulette, Blackjack, Dragon Tiger, Sic Bo, Andar Bahar, Teen Patti — according to established rules. You watch the game unfold on camera; the outcome depends on physical cards, spin wheels, or dice, not software. Slot games and other automated titles use a Random Number Generator (RNG), a certified algorithm that ensures every spin outcome is unpredictable and independent. RNG-based games carry an RTP (Return to Player) percentage — a statistical measure indicating the average payout over a very large number of plays. For example, a slot with returns an average of 96 units per 100 units wagered over millions of spins. RTP is not a guaranteed personal outcome; individual sessions vary widely. All our slot providers — PG Soft, Quickspin, Yggdrasil, Big Time Gaming — use certified RNG systems audited by independent laboratories. Live-dealer games have no RTP percentage; outcomes depend on dealer actions and physical events.</p>

 <h3>KYC verification process</h3>
 <p>We at Robopragma Pro require KYC verification to comply with anti-money-laundering regulations and confirm your eligibility. During sign-up, you provide your full legal name, date of birth, email, and phone number. Before your first withdrawal, we ask you to upload an identity document (passport, national ID, or driver's licence) and proof of address (utility bill or bank statement dated within the last 90 days). Our verification team reviews these documents within subject to verification during standard hours. Acceptable documents must be clear, legible, and match the name registered on your account. If your documents are unclear or do not match, we request resubmission. Once verified, your account is fully activated for deposits and withdrawals. Verification is a one-time process — you do not need to reverify for each transaction. If your address changes, update it in your account settings and resubmit proof of address if requested. KYC is mandatory for all users; accounts that do not complete verification cannot withdraw funds.</p>

 <h3>User feedback and review channels</h3>
 <p>We at Robopragma Pro encourage users to share feedback about their experience. Your input helps us improve our platform — from payment methods to game variety to support quality. You can leave feedback directly in your account settings or contact our English support team via live chat, email, or help centre. Online reviews from independent sources may mention Robopragma Pro — read multiple sources and consider both positive and critical perspectives to form your own view. No single review represents the complete picture; individual experiences vary based on payment method, game preference, regional factors, and personal expectations. We do not claim specific star ratings or rankings — user satisfaction depends on your own priorities and circumstances. If you experience an issue — a delayed withdrawal, a game glitch, a billing question — report it to our support team immediately. We investigate complaints and work toward resolution. Your honest feedback, whether positive or constructive, is valuable to our team.</p>
